ygData.messageBody:
the ogres in West Karanas

Chief Goonda 35th level
Ogre Shaman 30th level
5 Ogre Guards(SK's) are 25 each, not too mention their pets.

Grab a druid maybe 28+ level and just have him cast harmony a few times on
the camp then pull Goonda or the shaman out. Goonda has MULTIPLE nice
items from rings to earrings and belts to bracelets.

Becarefull of pulling the whole camp. The ogre guards will harm touch
multiple times, and the shaman keeps the entire camp buffed and SoWed.

Cormik
Druid on Cazic Thule
26th Rank
